libxdg-basedir: The XDG Base Directory Specification defines where should 
libxdg-basedir: user files be looked for by defining one or more base 
libxdg-basedir: directories relative in with they should be located.
libxdg-basedir: This library implements functions to list the directories 
libxdg-basedir: according to the specification and provides a few 
libxdg-basedir: higher-level functions.
